    <item>
      <title>Cboe 的徐先生表示，股市抛售是由流动性驱动的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/stock-market-selloff-is-liquidity-driven-cboe-s-xu-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cboe 衍生品市场情报主管 Mandy Xu 表示，周五的市场抛售更多是由基本面因素推动的，而非周一的抛售。她在彭博电视台发表讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-05/stock-market-selloff-is-liquidity-driven-cboe-s-xu-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:37:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
