      <title>吸金数十亿美元的科技 ETF 惨遭 60% 亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/tech-etfs-that-drew-billions-are-battered-by-losses-hitting-60</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，交易员投入了数十亿美元押注科技股大幅反弹。如今，他们杠杆率较高的 ETF 头寸在市场全面崩盘中遭受重创。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/tech-etfs-that-drew-billions-are-battered-by-losses-hitting-60</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:34:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球市场危机加剧，大宗商品面临危机蔓延</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/commodities-face-contagion-as-global-market-meltdown-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着全球金融危机的扩大，从铜、黄金到原油等大宗商品价格大幅下跌，交易员纷纷套现获利，并在工业原材料市场进行新的看跌押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/commodities-face-contagion-as-global-market-meltdown-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:25:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
