      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 14:21:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大陆集团考虑分拆汽车零部件业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/continental-weighs-spinning-off-struggling-automotive-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大陆集团可能会将其陷入困境的汽车零部件业务与更为成功的轮胎业务分开，这将成为这家德国公司 152 年历史上最大的重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/continental-weighs-spinning-off-struggling-automotive-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 11:40:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球股市陷入风险抛售：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着对全球最大经济体增长放缓的担忧加剧，全球市场高风险领域的崩溃进一步加深，股市暴跌，交易员纷纷涌向安全的债券市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
